\vert\vert Ax + b \vert\vert \leqslant 1
\vert\vert Ax + b \vert\vert^2 \leqslant 1
\vert\vert Ax + b \vert\vert^2 = (Ax+b, Ax+b) = (Ax+b)^{T}(Ax+b) = (x^{T}A^{T} + b^{T})(Ax+b) = x^{T}(A^{T}A)x+ x^{T}A^{T}b + b^{T}Ax  + b^{T}b=x^{T}(A^{T}A)x + 2(b^{T}A)x + (b^{T}b) = x^{T} \tilde{A} x + 2\tilde{b}^{T}x + \tilde{C}
